      "author": "PixelAnay",
      "description": "Full architectural overhaul of the LLAMA Chat plugin.\n\n**What's new in v4.0.0:**\n- Critical bug fixes: replace_block occurrence selection, undo for delete/move/rename, path traversal protection\n- Security: vault content sandboxed against prompt injection, real user confirmation for destructive ops\n- Performance: debounced streaming render, cached vault map, incremental DOM updates, chunked full-text search\n- Architecture: ChatView refactored from 1200 to ~430 lines, 8 new focused modules extracted\n- UX: token budget bar, dynamic welcome chips, selective undo history panel, context-build status label\n- TypeScript strict mode enabled (0 errors)",
      "draft": false,
      "name": "4.0.0",
